HTC CORP June Sales Rise 87.25% (Table) : 2498 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-03T10:45:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/htc-corp-june-sales-rise-87-25-table-2498-tt.html
HTC CORP (2498)  said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 87.25% to NT$44,675,006,000 from NT$23,857,984,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales           44,675,006       23,857,984  
YOY%              87.25%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales          223,678,248       98,229,763  
YOY%             127.71% 
=================================================================
 